Global Vehicle Parking Meter Market Insights
Vehicle Parking Meter Market size was valued at USD 3.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 5.6 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.8% from 2024 to 2030.

Vehicle Parking Meter Market Overview
The global vehicle parking meter market was valued at USD 5.12 billion in 2024 and is projected to reach USD 9.32 billion by 2030, growing at a compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 9.12% from 2025 to 2030. This market's growth is driven by the increasing demand for efficient urban traffic management, technological advancements in smart parking meters, and rising urbanization globally. The integration of IoT-based systems, contactless payments, and digital parking solutions is transforming the way parking is managed, leading to improved convenience and reduced traffic congestion. As cities grow more densely populated, the need for efficient and sustainable parking solutions has become paramount, further driving the demand for modern parking meters.

